{"tid":1631503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"個問題係 唔私了 唔裝修, 勇武仔仔出黎可以有咩搞？","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:40:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:05:01.000Z","uid":120814,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d3e59e08b020a210f6802f2eac3706a744d9683e","tid":1631503,"uid":120814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:40:22.000Z","msg":"先唔講遊行集會佔領死守<br />\n<br />\n圍狗屋 你地話無用<br />\n<br />\n軍營 唔衝得<br />\n<br />\n咁即係淨返同狗隻對峙, 但係<br />\n<br />\n打狗 裝備差距太大 你燒佢未必燒得死 佢拎槍打到你殘廢 仲唔一定下下有落單狗<br />\n<br />\n佢唔開真槍都下下tg 橡膠海綿彈 水炮車<br />\n<br />\n你拎磚遠攻 佢又頭盔又盾<br />\n你近攻佢一隊人衝埋黎制服你<br />\n<br />\n同狗打根本回報低 成本大<br />\n<br />\n私了裝修 打完爆完就閃 <br />\n你話形象差 對唔準目標 ok<br />\n咁比d提議勇武抗爭點持續落去？<br />\n淨係快閃堵路？<br />\n街坊屌下狗唱下肥媽就算？"},{"pid":"dafaa1cdc9de2a7ffa8ea5700b1034c7657252b6","tid":1631503,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:42:41.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n記唔記得當初應承過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈都唔割</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣洗地</span></strong></span>開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fd3ea78f1038604258b440b3da99d324429e73d3","tid":1631503,"uid":120814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:01:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64474dffbe2f0ad5bd712f2fb11a623ace16c5c9","tid":1631503,"uid":120814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:03:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f2922d1efc24f3d69e274f1ab587cfaa914d5e9","tid":1631503,"uid":179